VR, but with the addition of being able to gently steer your plane mid-flight. Eight lusciously designed levels will test your skills with increasing difficulty, occluded targets and cross-winds, but there is no game over so you can enjoy the challenge at your own leisure. Gradually work your way through the valley to unearth the mysterious and wondrous history of the land.\n\nWinner of the Famitsu Media Highlight Award at BitSummit in Kyoto, Japan 2017.", "short_description": "Glide enchanted paper planes across a desolate fantasy landscape and hit distant targets to bring life back to the world. Use your planes to rejuvenate the entire valley and cure the sickness that has left it barren and decayed. Enjoy the perfectly simulated feel of throwing a paper plane in VR across eight lusciously designed levels that will test your skills with increasing difficulty. Gradually work your way through the valley to unearth the mysterious and wondrous history of the land."}]}, "developer_name": "Vitei Backroom", "developer_privacy_policy_url": null, "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.viteibackroom.com/legal.html", "publisher_name": "Vitei Backroom", "support_website_url": "http://www.viteibackroom.com/", "website_url": "http://www.viteibackroom.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "CASUAL", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "de", "ja", "zh_CN", "zh_TW", "ko", "it", "es", "ru", "pt_BR"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "461936765395891"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, 